name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On April 12, a man stabbed another man in the street near Wanda Plaza in Zhangzhou, Fujian. The video showed a man stabbing another man in the street, and a woman nearby was trying to stop the man from stabbing him. A staff member of the Longwen District Public Security Bureau said that the incident happened suddenly, and the police responded quickly after receiving the alarm. They controlled the man on the spot and sent one injured man to the hospital, and the injured man is still being rescued.
